    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PresetBrowser.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015469308&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=497\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392626287/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015469308&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1344\" data-width=\"2054\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"622821423\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PresetBrowser.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392626287\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"ab2c9ee6-651f-4289-8748-de89585ff1e3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015469308&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=994 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/PresetBrowser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015469308&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=497 1x\"></span><p>RenderMan offers a highly efficient and creative workflow when paired with Substance Painter for texturing and lookdev.</p><p>Introducing …. the RenderMan for Substance Painter plugin, which allows artists to save their materials directly from Painter into the RenderMan Preset browser, which you can then import onto your models in your chosen DCC</p><p>The plugin handles all texture conversion, offers the option to create a PxrSurface or Lama Shader, and saves the material as a preset.</p><p>The workflow eliminates the need for manual node building and shading, handling everything for you. </p><p>All you have to do is focus on creating beautiful materials in Substance Painter!</p><p /><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/prman-pixar/RfSP\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015359009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392626287/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015359009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"622788642\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392626287\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"ee2d2c25-ecd4-48cd-a7c0-234dcc12a32f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015359009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392626287/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760015359009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\"></span></a><p /><iframe class=\"youtube-player conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"c44311b0-17ae-490f-9301-33f